social_posts.post_text:
We are so excited to have Featured Guest, @gglindsayelyse, at UwU Con 2023! 😍Lindsay Elyse is a cosplayer, streamer, gamer, and content creator from Phoenix, Arizona. She started cosplaying in 2005 and has since attended conventions all over the world. She makes her own costumes and is well-versed in sewing, armor making, and 3D printing.

In addition to cosplay, Lindsay also streams full-time on Kick and part time on Twitch. She's done official launch day streams and provided early access content for upcoming game releases alongside companies like Bethesda, Gearbox, Microsoft, CD Projekt Red and Square Enix. She also combines her two passions by cosplaying on stream while playing each character's respective game.

UwU Con is THREE DAYS AWAY! 🥳 Meet Lindsay at the Quickscope Apparel Booth (A1), on Oct. 27-29 at @legacyparkaz in Mesa, AZ. Badges are available at uwucon.com! 💕
At @uwuconaz this weekend at the @quickscopeapparel booth! Come see us to the left of the main entrance 💕
